Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:51.25,OP-TC,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}片尾名單過後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:54.04,OP-TC,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}無論等待多久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:57.41,OP-TC,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}始終不曾上演期待的後續
